1939;;Invitation to Happiness;;American;;Wesley Ruggles;;Irene Dunne, Fred MacMurray, Charlie Ruggles;;drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Invitation_to_Happiness;;Albert 'King' Cole is a talented heavyweight boxer who has potential to achieve the championship. At least his trainer, Henry 'Pop' Hardy thinks so. Hardy brings in his friend Mr. Wayne to sponsor Cole. Cole meets Mr. Wayne's daughter, Eleanor who is arrogant, but Cole manages to catch Eleanor's attention. Will they overcome their differences and obstacles and be together?